{
  "stem": "3022.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And he took the bottle of water, didn't even touch it with his lips.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He turned to the next to him, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and he says, drink [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So there's enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Drink, my child, but just a little bit, so there's enough for the next one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And this act of his froze the whole car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And that bottle of water kept passing on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Even after it was empty, it kept passing on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And it was like something-- we became transformed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "His act of self-sacrifice [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] returned to us our dignity.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And when we finally got to Flossenburg on the fourth day, I think for that time, for that moment, we were different people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Reb Meyer expired in the Camp Flossenburg about a month before liberation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "But to many of those who were in this particular car, his act was something that was a beacon of hope and faith.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "We got to the Camp of Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was a revelation to us, because it was the first camp in Germany where the Jews were not anymore.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "We arrived there on Sunday, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "We walked out from the cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And it took us a while before our legs were able to function.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And they marched us to the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And it was on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And we saw people working outside, tending the gardens and the flowers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "There were inmates.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And some of them told us that the whole Austrian government is there [GERMAN], and the Austrian government was incarcerated over there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And we were brought into what they called-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] what do you call-- when they quarantine barracks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "We were stripped naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And for four days and four nights, we were kept naked.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
